CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: LegalZoom.com, Inc. is an American online legal technology and services company launched in 2001.It helps its customers create legal documents without necessarily having to hire a lawyer. Available documents include wills and living trusts, business formation documents, copyright registrations, and trademark applications. The company also offers attorney referrals and registered agent services.
